name: Photo booth For a Cause - Typhoon Yolanda
description:
Typhoon Yolanda/Haiyan is one of the strongest storms to hit the Philippines, killing at least 3000 people in that country. They desperately need our HELP and together we can help them rebuild their community. 

From now till the end of December Biluso will donate $25 of every sale towards the typhoon victims.

Own our Limited wrap edition booth and help for a good cause. 


Trivia:
Biluso is one of the barios of the town Silang Cavite, Philippines which 25% of their population originated from Samar and Leyte which are the main areas affected by this super typhoon.

name: Portable iPad Photo booth DIY kit  - IPAD NOT INCLUDED
description:
THE IPAD PHOTO BOOTH- works great for any party, wedding, or corporate event etc.. The booth comes with a tripod stand but can also be permanently mounted on a wall great for boutiques or shops. 

Available in white or black at this price, but more color options will be available soon. 


Included is:
• Photo booth Case
• Key lockable 
• Tripod stand 

You will need:
Ipad 2 or newer
Download the Photobooth App for $1.99

FAQ

Q. Can I print the images?
A. Our Photobooth app gives you the ability to print (single pic only) via air port printers, or any photo printer via third party application. 

Q. Can I post to any social media?
A. Yes Facebook, twitter or email (instagram coming soon)

Q. How much does it weight?
A. The booth with the ipad is under 12 lbs

Q. Can I add my company logo? 
A. Yes we can wrap the case with your own design for a small fee 

Q. What printer do you recommend for beginners? 
A. The epson picture mate is just under $149 and it's a great sub dyed printer, it can be used for any event. 

Q. What if i'm doing a long event can I get a power strip install in the booth so that i can charge my ipad? 
A. Yes of course we can install it along with a mouse hole so you can run your cables in and out.

name: Portable Photo Booth Windows 8 version
description:
Photo booth your next event

Our popular Patent Pending tablet booths have become a huge hit! We offer the most portable Photo booth in the planet and not to mention the most affordable. Thinking of hiring a photo booth for your next event? why hire one when you can own one, all you need is to own a tablet. This photo booth shell can be made to accommodate any windows 8 tablet ( iPad versions are also available).

With the use of our Photo Booth software you can take pictures, add effects, print and share on Facebook. 

This listing will include:

• Very Light Photobooth case
• Key lockable Keeps your tablet safe
• Tripod

You will only need: 
• Windows 8 Tablet
• Download our Professional Photo Booth app only $7.99
• Photo Printer if you wish to print

About the APP

Q: Can I choose a layout? 
A: Yes the app comes with over 15 different preset layouts 

Q: Can I add a logo or text to my Photo layout?
A: Absolutely there's 5 standard layouts that can be customized with your own logo or text

Q: How much is it to for updates? 
A: All of our updates are free !!! 

Q: I have a windows RT tablet will it work? 
A: Yes the application will also work on Windows RT tablet

Q: I would like to know if my printer will work? 
A: Message us will let you know. 

Q: I will do a event that's more then 5hrs, is there room for a power plug to keep my tablet charging? 
A: Absolutely we made sure we left some room for a power strip and there's a optional cable hole on the bottom as well so you can run your extension cord. 

Q: How soon can I get my unit? 
A: All units are individually handmade by us in our Los Angeles Shop, please allow one week for build. We stock units from time to time, please message us for availability. 

Q: Can I add a logo on my case? 
A: Of course, we offer logo plates and we also offer logo engraving directly onto the case. 

Q: Is there some sort of lock that keeps my tablet safe in the case, and how is the door lock? 
A: The tablet is being held by padded wood blocks which can be move around incase you upgrade to a new tablet. It's also key lockable so it wont go anywhere. 

These are just a few of the questions we have answer in the past please feel free to message us with any questions you might have. 

Thank you for supporting handmade items.
